## Mount

---


[Bi-entity Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/bientity_action_types/mount)

Mounts the actor entity onto the target entity.

Type ID: `origins:mount`

---

### Examples

```json
"bientity_action": {
    "type": "origins:mount"
}
```
